Automation Framework
==============================
1. Java ==> programming language of the framework. It is developed on java pl.

2. Maven ==> build and dependency management tool

3. Selenium ==> Library that interacts our java with the browser, talk to the website

4. JUnit ==> assertions, running tests

5. Cucumber ==> BDD testing tool, writing tests, running tests, reporting tests, building test suites

6. Jenkins ==> Continous Integration tool

7. Git ==> Source code management






 TestNG Automation Framework ==> more annotations, parallel testing, multi btowser testing, parallel
								   multi browser testing.
								   
 